snippet.title: 17 Jag Mein Ghor Andhera - Maharaj Charan Singh - Punjabi Satsang - CC
snippet.description:
This is a satsang given by Hazur Maharaj Charan Singh in Punjabi language. Hazur covers all the important themes to inspire the sangat (congregation) to continue their efforts in meditation. He enjoins us to understand the purpose of life and the importance of seeing past this temporary, illusionary world and focus our attention on what is permanent.

This video is published by Radha Soami Satsang Beas. You may visit our official website at: http://www.rssb.org
